name: NutritionalStatus
title: Nutritional Status
description: April 2024 Revised to be consistent with NCPT problem list
purpose: (Clinical Focus: A Value Set of SNOMED CT codes representing nutrition diagnoses (problems).),(Data Element Scope: Data for nutrition problem(s) identification.),(Inclusion Criteria: Nutrition problems that reveal person's immediate or longer-term nutritional status.),(Exclusion Criteria: Nutrition assessment data and interventions.)
